{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the vibrant world of Perino Candy Buster, an action-packed arcade game that combines classic Block Breaker gameplay with a delightful twist! Join Perino and friends on a whimsical adventure filled with colorful graphics, engaging stories, and competitive local multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319050/extras/screens_02.png?t=1733572904\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Charming Graphics</strong>: Immerse yourself in a beautifully crafted world bursting with cute characters and vibrant environments that bring the fun to life!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engaging Story Mode</strong>: Follow Porino on a quest to save his cake! Overcome challenging levels and unlock unique power-ups as you progress through a captivating narrative.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Arcade PvP</strong>: Challenge your friends in thrilling local multiplayer matches! Test your skills in fast-paced gameplay where the goal is to outlast your opponents and score the highest points.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exciting Mini-Games</strong>: Take a break from the main adventure with four unlockable mini-games that offer different gameplay mechanics and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319050/extras/screens_05.png?t=1733572904\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319050/extras/screens_04.png?t=1733572904\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Are you ready to bounce into fun? Grab your paddle, gather your friends, and let the ball-busting adventures